---
title: Open-Faced Steak Sandwich with Caramelized Onion and Tomato Caprese Salad
description: Sweet and savoury caramelized onions top this juicy open-faced steak sammie. We've paired it with a classic Caprese salad as a light and refreshing complement to this dish!
